---
import WikiLayout from '../../layouts/WikiLayout.astro';
---
<WikiLayout title="Locations" section="locations" description="Explore the world of Davy Jones' Deckhand — islands, voyage routes, and key locations in this pirate roguelike deckbuilder. Each island unlocks new encounters, vendors, and progression.">
  <div class="wiki-content">
    <h1>Locations</h1>
    <p>
      Davy Jones' Deckhand takes place across a freely explorable world map. Islands serve as progression
      hubs — places to explore, spend coin, meet NPCs, upgrade your ship, and plan the next voyage.
    </p>
    <p>
      Voyages between islands are procedurally generated based on the distance between origin and destination,
      the biomes you'll travel through, and your chosen weapon. Longer voyages mean more encounters… and harder bosses at the end.
    </p>
    <div class="stub-notice">Location data will be added as the game develops.</div>

    <h2>Notable Locations</h2>
    <table class="locations-table">
      <thead><tr><th></th><th>Location</th><th>Notes</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td class="location-img-cell"><a href="/locations/the-locker"><img src="/images/locations/locker.png" alt="The Locker" class="location-img" /></a></td>
          <td class="location-name"><a href="/locations/the-locker">The Locker</a></td>
          <td>Where Tom wakes after each death. Site of narrative cutscenes and home to you-know-who.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="location-img-cell"></td>
          <td class="location-name">The Turtle-Island Spa</td>
          <td>The Fountain of Youth day-spa on the back of a primordial turtle. Grace O'Malley's annual destination.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="location-img-cell"></td>
          <td class="location-name">Nosy Bugle</td>
          <td>An all-but-abandoned outpost where Tom washes up after his first resurrection.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="location-img-cell"><a href="/locations/sainte-marie"><img src="/images/locations/sainte-marie.jpg" alt="Sainte Marie" class="location-img" /></a></td>
          <td class="location-name"><a href="/locations/sainte-marie">Sainte Marie</a></td>
          <td>A bustling trading port.</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>
</WikiLayout>

<style>
  .location-img-cell {
    width: 160px;
    padding: 0.4rem 0.75rem 0.4rem 0;
    vertical-align: middle;
  }

  .location-img {
    width: 160px;
    max-width: none;
    aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    display: block;
  }

  .location-name {
    font-weight: 700;
    white-space: nowrap;
    vertical-align: middle;
  }
</style>
